Evocation [Cold]
Level: Sor/Wiz 3
Components: V,S
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: Medium (100 ft + 10 ft/level)
Area: 30-ft radius burst
Duration: Instantaneous
Saving Throw: Reflex half
Spell Resistance: Yes

A hail of magical ice-chunks erupts from a point in space.  The chunks fly in all directions, hitting everything within the burst.  The pelting of ice deals 1d4 points of cold damage +1 point of bludgeoning damage per caster level, to a maximum of 10d4+10.